  <section class="my-64">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-6xl">FAQ</h2>
        <p class="text-2xl">If you have questions, we will endeavour to answer them!</p>
        <a class="button" href="https://github.com/itinershare/itinershare/issues/new/choose">Contact support team</a>
      </div>
      <div class="space-content">
        <Accordion>
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="Why does this exist?" open>
            <p>
              When creating this app, we were looking for an easy way that people could share plans through a single
              point. Travel, hotels, restaurants, all organised through one app. That is how itinershare came to be.
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="Can you add a feature I want?">
            <p>
              It is most likely possible! If you contact our support team through email, we can add almost any feature
              to the roadmap! (within reason)
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="What are the costs?">
            <p>
              In short, storage costs money. We would love to keep the entire app free, but that just isn't feasible. We
              have a generous free tier for a small weekend away but for longer trips with more data needed, we need to
              be able to pay for the space to be able to accomodate that.
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
        </Accordion>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
